---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Srenix &mdash; Privacy"
  description="Privacy policy for srenix.ai: static site, no analytics, no cookies, no tracking, self-hosted fonts, no third-party requests."
>
  <PageHero eyebrow="Legal" title="Privacy policy" />

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pb-20">
    <div class="space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
      <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500">Last updated: 2026-06-11</p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">The short version</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          This website does not collect personal data. There is nothing to
          opt out of, because there is nothing to opt in to.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">What this site does (and doesn't do)</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1.5 pl-5">
          <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">Static site.</strong> srenix.ai is a statically generated site. There are no user accounts, forms, or server-side sessions.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">No analytics.</strong> We run no analytics — first-party or third-party.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">No cookies.</strong> The site sets no cookies.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">No tracking.</strong> No tracking pixels, fingerprinting, ad tech, or session recording.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">No third-party requests.</strong> All assets — including fonts — are self-hosted and served from this domain. Your browser talks only to srenix.ai when viewing this site.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Like any web server, our hosting infrastructure may produce standard
          access logs (IP address, user agent, requested URL) for operational
          and security purposes. These are not used for profiling and are not
          shared with third parties.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">The Srenix product</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          The Agentic SRE software runs entirely inside your own
          infrastructure and ships with zero telemetry by default — it does not
          phone home. This policy covers the website only; how you operate the
          software in your cluster is under your control.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">GDPR and data requests</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Because this site collects no personal data, there is no personal
          data for us to access, correct, export, or delete. If you believe we
          hold personal data about you (for example, because you emailed us),
          contact us at the address below and we will handle your request
          promptly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Privacy questions:
          <a class="font-medium text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-700 dark:text-accent-400" href="mailto:hello@srenix.ai">hello@srenix.ai</a>.
          Security reports:
          <a class="font-medium text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-700 dark:text-accent-400" href="mailto:security@srenix.ai">security@srenix.ai</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">Changes</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          If this site ever starts collecting anything, this page will say so
          before it happens, with a changelog entry and an updated date above.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
